      <textAnnotation id="sid-4AFE590F-3B7B-4CB4-8385-A6F4A1F96444" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Example- Block/Remove Supplier</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4422B709-AD20-4DE8-8C5C-8C8EA2182B45" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Targeted recognition (any form)
Example: supplier dinner, supplier day, epic programs</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0F8D335B-6B18-41EF-B499-3C4E15EB107E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Process Description:
Enhance and develop on-going supplier relationships and provide timely feedback of performance data to suppliers. This feedback could be about their performance in assessment programs or in an ongoing supply of goods/services. For established suppliers, involve both superior and sub-standard performers in the communication. Reward outstanding performance, if only through annual recognition with a letter of commendation. Elicit corrective action through this feedback to sub-standard performers.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8E46BD16-3CBE-411E-902A-8B71376A74F9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Boundary apps:
*Online supplier report card
*Supplier 360 (SAM,SDM)
*PowerBi dashboards</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-68D98CEF-CFE4-4E5D-8A43-989FC9763887" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: Procure To Pay
Process Group: Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-040-220 Provide Feedback to Suppliers Regularly
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B2514C48-50FC-4A6B-9224-C58300D73A5B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Nageswaran, Rohan &lt;rohan.nageswaran@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect 
those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
   <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="sid-95a3e001-09d3-4885-9754-4bb62b8b3cb7" name="PM-040-220_Provide Feedback to Suppliers Regularly">
